doctype html
html
  head
    meta(charset='utf-8')
    meta(name='viewport', content='user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1, minimum-scale=1, width=device-width, height=device-height, target-densitydpi=device-dpi')
    title Singular-TimeZones
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='/css/style.css')
  body
    #home
      img(src='img/home.jpg')
    #app
      .header
        .headerContent
          .addZones.icon-zones
          .addModal
            .addTriangle
            .addContent
          .title
            span.singular.light Singular
            span.timeZones.bold TimeZones
          .aboutUs.icon-about
          .aboutModal
            .aboutTriangle
            .aboutContent
              .aboutText
                h3 About us
                p
                  | In our day-to-day we need to make conference and videoconference calls with different cities around the world. We could not find any useful tool for that. 
                  span
                    a(href='https://twitter.com/thomasfuchs') @thomasfuchs'
                  |  everytimezone.com is the best one we found.
                p
                  | Besides, it was not very useful for us since we wanted to be able to change cities. I don't necessarily know which cities share a time zone. Also, we needed an APP.
                p
                  | Based on Thomas concept, and within the University internship framework with 
                  span
                    a(href='https://twitter.com/AlexRecursive') Alex Unger
                  | , we decided to launch the free app SingularTimeZone for the community and check if it is helpful in their daily work.
                p
                  | I hope you like it.
                p
                  | Thanks Thomas for your vision and Alex for your hard work during your internship.
                p
                  a(href='http://singularfactory.com') singularfactory.com team
      .content
        .yourTimeZone
          .yourTime
            .yourTag
              #your_time.tagTime.bold
              .infoText Your local time
            .yourTriangle
            #line.line.yourLine
        .infoBarsZone
        .moveZone
          .currentTime
            .currentTag
              #current_time.tagTime.bold
              .infoText Current local time
            .currentTriangle
            .line.currentLine
          .barsZone
        .adds
          .addsContent
            .addsClose
              .icon-highlight-remove
    script(src='vendor/overlaps/jquery.overlaps.js')
    script(src='js/main.js')